freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: For some reason, my food sensitivities and allergic reactions were significantly improved temporarily after the first vaccination. I thought it was coincidence, but it wad the same story again after the 2nd vaccination. I've barely needed oral antihistamines.  Sounds crazy, but it's true.
